#Athletics: For the first time at the Pacific Games, four [[Disabled sports|parasport]] events were included: Men's Shot Put – seated throw, Women's Shot Put – seated throw, Men's Javelin – ambulatory, and Men's 100m – ambulatory.<ref name = para-2011>{{cite web
|date= 21 May 2011
|title= Handisport included for New Caledonia
