'''Jamhuri Stadium''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Morogoro]], [[Tanzania]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and serves as the home venue for [[Moro United]]. It currently holds 10,000 people.<ref name="stadia"/>
